## Comparison Table (for paper)

| Method | Type | Privacy | Robustness | Threshold Tunable | In Our Paper |
|--------|------|---------|------------|-------------------|--------------|
| FedAvg | Plain | ❌ | ❌ | N/A | ✅ Baseline |
| Multi-Krum | Robust | ❌ | ✅ | f param | ✅ Baseline |
| Krum | Robust | ❌ | ✅ | f param | ✅ Baseline |
| Trimmed Mean | Robust | ❌ | ✅ | beta | ✅ Baseline |
| **SSS (ours, l=1)** | SecAgg | ✅ | ✅ | **✅ threshold** | Ours |
| **PSSS (ours, l>1)** | SecAgg | ✅ | ✅ | **✅ + efficient** | **Main contribution** |

