## Verification Plan

```bash
# Step 1: Fix and verify PSSS math
python test_packed_sharing.py

# Step 2: End-to-end MNIST test
python run_experiment.py --experiment mnist --cfg_file_path data/mnist_10/cfg.json \
  --n_rounds 5 --secure_aggregation --threshold 3

# Step 3: Full benchmark on MNIST
python benchmark.py --cfg_file_path data/mnist_10/cfg.json --experiment mnist --n_rounds 20

# Step 4: Threshold sweep
python threshold_analysis.py --experiment mnist --cfg_file_path data/mnist_10/cfg.json

# Step 5: CIFAR runs
python benchmark.py --cfg_file_path data/cifar10_20/cfg.json --experiment cifar10 --n_rounds 30
```
